Package: SK4FGA
Type: Package
Title: Scott-Knott for Forensic Glass Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Toby Hayward, James Curran
Maintainer: Toby Hayward <tobyhayward13@gmail.com>
Description: Functions for use when comparing features of glass fragment samples and determining their relation. The package exercises the Scott-Knott algorithm for the grouping problem and incorporate modifications for small sample glass fragment analysis. Build currently supports both univariate using the refractive index (ri), and multivariate analysis. 
